# Maintainer-only template generator for the AI-agent rules kit.
# Holds this repo's real literals (workspace path, sf alias, org brand
# name) as find-replace TARGETS that it strips out when populating
# scripts/initagentrulespy/templates/. Those literals can't be
# genericized without breaking tokenization, so the script stays local.
# The committed/shareable kit is just init.py + templates/.
scripts/initagentrulespy/_sync.py

# Sequential org-mirror retrieve logs (see docs/sf-org-mirror-retrieve.md).
# These are transient per-run build artefacts; their summaries get committed
# under changes/git/ instead. The single umbrella entry below covers both
# the active-run subdir (.retrieve-logs/current/) and each archived prior
# run (.retrieve-logs/archive/<TS>/).
.retrieve-logs/
